{
  "stem": "8361.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They let us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From Russia, they let us go to Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We said, we're going to Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Poland was, at that time, communist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they let us go back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when we came to Poland, there were pogroms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were killing Jews after the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So we tried to get into-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there were boys from Israel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was called the You can write it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were killing Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Polacks.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were making pogroms that we couldn't stay there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went to-- the guys from Israel helped us to get to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we got to Czechoslovakia, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they let-- they-- the Red Cross came already there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a place where everybody came, like a transit place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from there, they took us with train-- with the train to DP camps in Austria.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Austria.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not a DP camp, but just a transit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anybody stopped there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We couldn't stay.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew already everything, what was happening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I wouldn't go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was even afraid to go there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because some people went, and they told us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew that nobody's alive, because I didn't tell you that I was writing to my town, to all the friends, Christian friends, to tell me--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1944.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it was already free from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So '44, '45, I was writing all the time and nobody answered.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But somehow, a Jewish girl was working already in the post office.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she got my letters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She knew who I was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she knew about my sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I told you my youngest sister escaped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
